chapter.title: SIMPLE BRAILLE TRACKING SHEETS
chapter.p: These all need to be tracked using a braille display. for NVDA and JASWS, go into the braille submenu and set the braille display OUTPUT to US Computer braille (it will not show correctly with either Grade 1 or Grade 2 UEB)
